</td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: VP</span><hr size=1> Ok, so now we have FA and Stasis saying VP is FCFS. I really wish these people could make up their minds. All the sanctimonious bullshit they chimed in about 3 months ago don't pertain to today I guess. <br>
<br>
The real point is this:<br>
<br>
Had you not done what you all preached about us doing 3 months ago, a GM would not have been ask in to survey what was happening, and this post would not even exist.<br>
<br>
Go back to that trophy on ass.com Aleolin and just count the posts where members of ALL the upper tier guilds state pretty bluntly that had they zoned in and found out that there was indeed a raid in progress in VP that they would have left and that is the proper thing to do in VP.<br>
<br>
This was not FCFS. This was a blatent leapfrog to MB a mob while a raid was doing a CR.<br>
<br>
Can it be any clearer than that?<br>
<br>
Let me put it this way. If you really had a case this would have been taken to ass.com where the prexus community would have lambasted you all just as hard as IV was lambasted 3 months ago.<br>
<br>
Either that or the PC's with a stick up their ass still about the first event will be quick to jump on your side.<br>
<br>
Do unto others is a far better approach than seeking revenge for something that you were not even involved with in the first place. <br>
<br>
As a matter of fact I would venture a guess that had FA not been there that day, everything would have turned out just fine. <br>
<br>
I never question my actions nor my character because I always try to do the right thing. Never in my life have I had to question the actions or character of others as much as I have done in this game.<br>
<br>
It was the immature attitude of &quot;I am here now, so i am not going to leave till I take something&quot; that started this. <br>
<br>
If you people can't even admit to that then who has yet to mature in the world of Norrath?<br>
<br>
Do tell. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=850.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=850.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=850.topic&index=0><img src=http://www.infinitusvindicat.com/images/f_addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=850.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm1.threadControl?topicID=850.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=850.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/finfinitusvindicatfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=850.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub79.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="infinitusvindicatfrm1">The Commons<option value="infinitusvindicatfrm9">OT Discussions and Debates<option value="infinitusvindicatfrm5">Screenshots<option value="infinitusvindicatfrm2">The Inner Sanctum<option value="infinitusvindicatfrm17">Guild Polici